data.description: Charming home located in the desirable neighborhood of BelAir at Carolina Lakes. Spacious open floorplan with tons of natural light throughout, beautiful wide plank hardwood floors on the main level, built in drop zone, dining room with updated light fixtures, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, freshly painted cabinets, granite countertops and tons of cabinet space for storage. Main level also has the laundry room, a full bedroom - perfect for an office/playroom/or guest bedroom and a full bathroom. Upstairs you'll find 2 additional bedrooms, a bathroom, an oversized bonus room and the primary bedroom and bathroom containing a garden tub, double vanity and large walk-in closet. Large oversized fenced in yard with patio and lots of trees for privacy. Convenient location near lots of shopping & restaurants.
